","id":"zettel.literature.bmad-analysis-phase","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260421171824","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":3,"offset":1433},"end":{"line":32,"column":28,"offset":1458},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260421171824"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":131,"column":3,"offset":12127},"end":{"line":131,"column":44,"offset":12168},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.literature.bmad-analysis-phase"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.ai-native","id":"zettel.moc.ai-native","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":3,"offset":330},"end":{"line":10,"column":44,"offset":371},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.literature.bmad-analysis-phase"}],"anchors":{"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka":{"type":"header","text":"Pertanyaan yang dibuka","value":"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2},"ringkasan-literatur":{"type":"header","text":"Ringkasan literatur","value":"ringkasan-literatur","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2},"ide-penting":{"type":"header","text":"Ide penting","value":"ide-penting","line":26,"column":0,"depth":2},"interpretasi":{"type":"header","text":"Interpretasi","value":"interpretasi","line":32,"column":0,"depth":2},"sumber":{"type":"header","text":"Sumber","value":"sumber","line":36,"column":0,"depth":2},"lihat-juga":{"type":"header","text":"Lihat juga","value":"lihat-juga","line":40,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"ae3bw38eg7l5p3ntry27x87","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"bmad-analysis-phase-sebagai-literature-note\">BMAD Analysis Phase sebagai literature note<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#bmad-analysis-phase-sebagai-literature-note\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\">Pertanyaan yang dibuka<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Apa tujuan utama BMAD analysis phase?</li>\n<li>Bagaimana phase ini menghindari planning premature?</li>\n<li>Mengapa review awal di BMAD dianggap epistemic filter?</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"ringkasan-literatur\">Ringkasan literatur<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#ringkasan-literatur\"></a></h2>\n<p>Halaman BMAD Analysis Phase menempatkan fase analisis sebagai epistemic filter sebelum PRD dan arsitektur. Tujuannya adalah menghentikan ketidakjelasan, mengidentifikasi asumsi, dan memvalidasi apakah ide siap dipindahkan ke fase engineering.</p>\n<p>Phase ini mencakup beberapa alat: brainstorming, market research, domain research, technical research, product brief, dan PRFAQ. Fase ini bukan sekadar riset; ia adalah upaya memastikan bahwa planning tidak dibangun di atas kabut.</p>\n<h2 id=\"ide-penting\">Ide penting<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#ide-penting\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Analisis awal harus memisahkan problem finding dari solutioning.</li>\n<li>BMAD menganggap ide lemah sebagai masalah sistemik, bukan sekadar kesalahan eksekusi.</li>\n<li>Evidence, asumsi, dan risiko harus dihadirkan sebelum dokumen requirement resmi.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"interpretasi\">Interpretasi<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#interpretasi\"></a></h2>\n<p>Catatan ini memperjelas bahwa BMAD tidak memulai workflow dari penulisan PRD. Ia memulai dari klarifikasi epistemik untuk membuat seluruh pipeline lebih tahan terhadap asumsi salah.</p>\n<h2 id=\"sumber\">Sumber<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#sumber\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.bmad-method.org/explanation/analysis-phase/\">https://docs.bmad-method.org/explanation/analysis-phase/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"lihat-juga\">Lihat juga<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#lihat-juga\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171457\">BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</a> — BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171823\">BMAD analysis phase sebagai epistemic filter sebelum PRD</a> — BMAD analysis phase sebagai epistemic filter sebelum PRD</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171824\">BMAD Product Brief vs PRFAQ: klarifikasi lembut versus pengujian adversarial</a> — BMAD Product Brief vs PRFAQ: klarifikasi lembut versus pengujian adversarial</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">bmad (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">analysis-phase (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">literature (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.ai-native\">MOC AI-native engineering</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"selection2link","taskC